What This Project Does

Simulates a 3-way traffic light:

Red → 5 seconds
Yellow → 2 seconds
Green → 5 seconds
Loop forever

---

Proteus Components

Add:
ATmega328P (not Arduino board)
3 LEDs (Red, Yellow, Green)
3 × 220Ω resistors
16 MHz crystal
2 × 22pF capacitors
5V supply

---

What’s Happening Here

DDRD → Sets PORTD pins as output
PORTD → Controls LED state
_delay_ms() → Software delay
Bit shifting → Controls specific pins
